wordageddon.model

Class GameSessionSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • wordageddon.model.GameSessionSummary

  • public class GameSessionSummary
extends java.lang.Object
    Data Transfer Object for game session statistics in the leaderboard. This class represents the essential data for displaying game sessions without needing the full GameSession object with questions.
